Backbone.js Presentation and The Tutorial (Turkish Language, with PHP)

v1 Directory: The oldest way to create a Guestbook application.
 - There is no Javascript power used.

v2 Directory: Invention of the AJAX.
 - Ajax has an advantage to make web easier, but not "complete easy".

v3 Directory: Invention of the JSON.
 - Reducing traffic, inventing hashtags to share links, but still not completed.

v4 Directory: Invention of the Javascript MVCs.
 - Back-end MVCs get popular. HTML5 is the power. And front-end needed a powerful framework.